{"tid":1406393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「沙盤推演」Be Water 會令警隊瘋狂","createTime":"2019-08-04T13:12:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T14:26:57.000Z","uid":52105,"like":127,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"4669ad1991f714204017075196f24886bc511b6b","tid":1406393,"uid":52105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:12:36.000Z","msg":"純沙盤推演　不喜勿屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n西環（同黃大仙）終於睇到大家be water<br />\n一小群勇武引左班防暴出黎<br />\nset好哂陣轉場走人<br />\nfull gear防暴被迫企定定俾街方屌<br />\n西環為例，一小隊長盾防暴企左成粒鐘俾街方恥笑<br />\n而勇武＋和理非就搭地鐵轉場去西環<br />\n<br />\n呢樣野暴露左警隊反應時間極慢<br />\n前線report一層層咁上去，以今日嘅reaction time黎講係一個鐘<br />\n警隊嘅冷氣軍師 commander 會面臨兩難：<br />\n<br />\n- 繼續用現有commanding system反應太慢，各區着火跟本指令傳得太慢，又要做risk assessment。高層要睇哂全局意思即係全局任何一個角落出事，佢都要咩鑊。作為明哲保身嘅大sir當然係play safe，等火頭完全熄滅先撤走滅火隊。<br />\n<br />\n- 一係就下放權力，俾警隊前線有更大自由度移動部隊，但在<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">高層眼中根本信唔過落場嗰班</span></span>，睇片所見，就算落場嘅inspector係講道理，佢班細做錯事（例如射記者）都焗住護短。俾班細嘅知道自己嘅immediate commander有權移動小隊，作反都似。<br />\n<br />\n所以呢。方向正確。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n勇武派、和理非、街方終於統一槍口對外。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a9d497c2940f274a1b83731637f2c935f9fa05d","tid":1406393,"uid":242083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:13:29.000Z","msg":"Hit and run<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"730b34d544579eee9c5d8d9362253d962f3e09c2","tid":1406393,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:13:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1405338/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1405338/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[804] 係堅尼地城/西環有需要落腳嘅手足入黎!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f98eff3b74eb7dda21fbda78731b4ca4cdd367d","tid":1406393,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:14:17.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"f18a78e3a9ea94a853a25635db880f602ab6abf8","tid":1406393,"uid":199640,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:14:50.000Z","msg":"老早都知佢地調動極慢，所以先咁多次話d人送頭之麻...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb0df9dae26f5f600a89b680936dbcba8f8ab523","tid":1406393,"uid":154486,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:15:52.000Z","msg":"最終結局係班細既情緒失控唔聽命令自己「隨機應變」，玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52ee578462c75fc267afcd2ce14a1faec1ab9feb","tid":1406393,"uid":263806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:16:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8912af95d72d211ed414a5ed320be4b60ffa1966","tid":1406393,"uid":52105,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f18a78e3a9ea94a853a25635db880f602ab6abf8","tid":1406393,"uid":199640,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:14:50.000Z","msg":"老早都知佢地調動極慢，所以先咁多次話d人送頭之麻...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:16:40.000Z","msg":"重點係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">高層眼中根本信唔過落場嗰班</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f6624293a3423efc20e532e920fc45870d3d8df","tid":1406393,"uid":265047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:18:27.000Z","msg":"推1，只要不送頭都是好建議，要推爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\